1
00:00:32,782 --> 00:00:33,783
SALVATION ARMY

2
00:00:33,867 --> 00:00:35,702
HANMI PHARMACY

3
00:00:51,301 --> 00:00:53,636
CAN WE MEET? UNDERAGE?
HOW'S 200,000 WON FOR THREE HOURS?

4
00:01:19,704 --> 00:01:21,081
-Excuse me.
-My gosh…

5
00:01:21,164 --> 00:01:23,792
I'm really sorry,
but can I borrow your phone?

6
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:25,043
I'm sorry.

7
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:29,923
Hi, I've lost my phone and--

8
00:01:30,006 --> 00:01:31,591
Sorry, my phone is dead…

9
00:01:55,281 --> 00:01:57,575
I'll be there soon. Yes.

10
00:01:58,743 --> 00:01:59,953
I have to go.

11
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:02,580
Hey, kid.

12
00:02:03,581 --> 00:02:04,707
Hold up.

13
00:02:10,964 --> 00:02:12,298
What is this?

14
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:15,301
Is this blood?

15
00:02:16,344 --> 00:02:17,971
No, it isn't…

16
